#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.bomber.appdata.xml:9
msgid "Bomber"
msgstr "Bomber"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.bomber.appdata.xml:10
msgid "Arcade Bombing Game"
msgstr "Arkádová bombardovacia hra"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.bomber.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"Bomber is a single player arcade game. The player is invading various cities "
"in a plane that is decreasing in height."
msgstr ""
"Bomber je arkádová hra pre jedného hráča. Hráč napáda rôzne mestá v "
"lietadle, ktoré klesá."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.bomber.appdata.xml:15
msgid ""
"The goal of the game is to destroy all the buildings and advance to the next "
"level. Each level gets a bit harder by increasing the speed of the plane and "
"the height of the buildings."
msgstr ""
"Cieľom hry je zničiť všetky budovy na postúpenie do ďalšej úrovne. Každá "
"úroveň je o niečo ťažšia zvýšením rýchlosti lietadla a výškou budov."

